00:43:29.990 --> 00:43:34.061 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎proving it’s a fake; 
it’s a corruption of God’s Word.

00:43:34.061 --> 00:43:38.799 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎And yet for centuries, 
the churches propagated the Trinity doctrine.

00:43:38.799 --> 00:43:40.934 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎As recently as the 19th century, 

00:43:40.934 --> 00:43:42.970 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
