00:49:55.842 --> 00:49:58.445 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎One problem was not having a good translation

00:49:58.445 --> 00:50:00.681 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎of the Holy Scriptures in Quechua. 

00:50:00.681 --> 00:50:03.450 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎The commonly used translations here in Peru

00:50:03.450 --> 00:50:06.219 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎omit God’s name in the main text. 

00:50:06.219 --> 00:50:09.389 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎It can be found in the glossary of some Bibles,

00:50:09.389 --> 00:50:11.925 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
