00:50:43.023 --> 00:50:47.394 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and they have to understand what it means.

00:50:47.394 --> 00:50:51.932 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎It was difficult for us
to use the Bible at the meetings,

00:50:51.932 --> 00:50:55.836 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎in the field ministry, and in our family worship.

00:51:07.347 --> 00:51:09.616 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎How could Jehovah’s great name be sanctified

00:51:09.616 --> 00:51:12.219 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎throughout this mountainous region? 

00:51:12.219 --> 00:51:14.721 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎How could the Quechua people get to know God

00:51:14.721 --> 00:51:18.258 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎when his name was hidden?

00:51:18.258 --> 00:51:19.726 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎The answer to our prayers came

00:51:19.726 --> 00:51:22.729 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎when Quechua congregations
throughout the country

00:51:22.729 --> 00:51:24.264 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎were invited to a special program

00:51:24.264 --> 00:51:27.834 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎on May 1, 2016. 

00:51:27.834 --> 00:51:30.303 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Imagine the great joy we felt
when Brother Jackson

00:51:30.303 --> 00:51:32.906 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎of the Governing Body
announced the release

00:51:32.906 --> 00:51:36.109 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎of the New World Translation
of the Christian Greek Scriptures

00:51:36.109 --> 00:51:38.378 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎in two Quechua languages!

00:51:38.378 --> 00:51:40.881 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Language number 136:

00:51:40.881 --> 00:51:44.017 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎It’s the Christian Greek Scriptures

00:51:44.017 --> 00:51:48.321 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎in Quechua Ayacucho! 

00:51:55.962 --> 00:51:59.232 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎But we also have number 137:

00:51:59.232 --> 00:52:02.002 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎It’s Quechua Cuzco! 

00:52:05.572 --> 00:52:09.509 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎What a wonderful gift we’ve received today!

00:52:12.279 --> 00:52:15.182 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎This new Quechua Bible

00:52:15.182 --> 00:52:18.718 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎is a grand victory for Jehovah’s great name. 

00:52:18.718 --> 00:52:22.823 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎God’s name is no longer hidden
from the Quechua people,

00:52:22.823 --> 00:52:25.692 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎giving them the precious opportunity

00:52:25.692 --> 00:52:30.831 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎to come to know our loving Creator, Jehovah.

00:52:53.887 --> 00:52:57.891 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎I feel proud to use our new Bible to teach 

00:52:57.891 --> 00:53:00.360 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎my family and neighbors Jehovah’s name. 

00:53:00.360 --> 00:53:02.329 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎I am thankful every day

00:53:02.329 --> 00:53:05.131 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎that Jehovah sent this good news to the mountains 

00:53:05.131 --> 00:53:07.133 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎to us who speak runa simi

00:53:07.133 --> 00:53:11.137 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎—the language of the people.

00:53:14.808 --> 00:53:18.011 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎It was a privilege 
to be at such a happy event

00:53:18.011 --> 00:53:20.013 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and to see our brothers’ joy

00:53:20.013 --> 00:53:22.549 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎when they received 
the Christian Greek Scriptures

00:53:22.549 --> 00:53:25.085 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎in two Quechua languages. 

00:53:25.085 --> 00:53:28.555 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎May they use their Bibles 
to draw close to Jehovah

00:53:28.555 --> 00:53:32.859 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and glorify his name in the Andes Mountains.

00:53:32.859 --> 00:53:34.995 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Our program now goes

00:53:34.995 --> 00:53:37.030 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎to the South Pacific,

00:53:37.030 --> 00:53:40.066 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎where we conclude 
with greetings from Tuvalu. 

00:53:41.635 --> 00:53:46.139 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Most of Tuvalu’s nine islands 
are ring-shaped coral atolls

00:53:46.139 --> 00:53:48.575 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎surrounding peaceful lagoons. 

00:53:48.575 --> 00:53:52.479 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎These small islands barely rise out of the sea. 

00:53:52.479 --> 00:53:55.782 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎On Funafuti, Tuvalu’s capital,

00:53:55.782 --> 00:53:59.152 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎the island is just wide enough in some places

00:53:59.152 --> 00:54:03.223 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎for the main road and a single house. 

00:54:03.223 --> 00:54:06.626 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎The motorbike is the preferred way 
to travel on the island. 

00:54:06.626 --> 00:54:11.064 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎So it’s good that our witnessing carts
come equipped with sturdy wheels.

00:54:12.265 --> 00:54:15.802 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Tuvalu has a busy remote translation office. 

00:54:15.802 --> 00:54:17.904 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎In 2011,

00:54:17.904 --> 00:54:21.207 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎the New World Translation 
of the Christian Greek Scriptures in Tuvaluan

00:54:21.207 --> 00:54:22.909 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎was released. 

00:54:22.909 --> 00:54:27.314 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎In October of last year, 
the complete Bible was released,

00:54:27.314 --> 00:54:30.150 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎making Tuvaluan 
the smallest language group

00:54:30.150 --> 00:54:33.086 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎to receive the New World Translation. 

00:54:33.086 --> 00:54:36.523 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎I was assigned to Tuvalu in 1979

00:54:36.523 --> 00:54:38.825 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and enjoyed the challenging task

00:54:38.825 --> 00:54:41.895 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎of helping to establish Tuvaluan translation. 

00:54:41.895 --> 00:54:45.598 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎There were 
only 3 other baptized publishers back then,

00:54:45.598 --> 00:54:48.234 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎but in 2017,

00:54:48.234 --> 00:54:52.939 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Tuvalu reported a peak of 125 publishers.

00:54:52.939 --> 00:54:55.608 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎They preach to a population

00:54:55.608 --> 00:54:58.611 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎of around 10,000 people.

00:54:58.611 --> 00:55:00.680 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Tuvaluans are warm and friendly,

00:55:00.680 --> 00:55:03.116 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and our brothers and sisters thoroughly enjoy 

00:55:03.116 --> 00:55:05.318 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎the time they can spend together. 

00:55:06.453 --> 00:55:10.090 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎They send their love 
and greetings from the South Pacific.

00:55:13.026 --> 00:55:15.328 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Alofa atu in Tuvaluan means

00:55:15.328 --> 00:55:17.731 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎“We send our love to you all.”

00:55:17.731 --> 00:55:21.901 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎We send them our love 
and pray for Jehovah’s continued blessing.

00:55:21.901 --> 00:55:24.938 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎This is JW Broadcasting

00:55:24.938 --> 00:55:28.942 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

